  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Probability_distribution_arm.Probability_distribution.variance">
The variance is a mathematical property of a probability distribution, and this attribute holds the value for the distribution.
<note number="14"> Variance is a measure of how much the outcomes vary about the mean.</note>
</ext_description>


